title: War of the Roses: He Hurt His Back Running
description: Monica saw a suspicious text message on her boyfriend's phone while he was showing her a cat video. He also claims to have hurt his back running, even though he rarely exercises. So what's really going on? Who was that text from and did he really hurt himself while running or by doing something else?
